OL,3,CPioneering treatment could save sight
OL,4,Cof chemical attack victims
OL,6,FLast week four men were jailed for a
OL,7,Ftotal of almost 120 years for their
OL,8,Froles in a spate of attacks on
OL,9,FTyneside that left one man dead and a
OL,10,Fwoman without her sight in one eye.
OL,12,FAccording to the Acid Survivors Trust
OL,13,FInternational (ASTI), it is women who
OL,14,Fare increasingly the target and in
OL,15,Fmany instances it is eyes that suffer
OL,16,Fthe most damage.
