OL,3,CPioneering treatment could save sight
OL,4,Cof chemical attack victims
OL,6,F"It's affecting the stem cells but you
OL,7,Fdon't have the expense of trying to
OL,8,Fgrow stem cells and introducing them
OL,9,Fto the patient - which is a therapy
OL,10,Fbut a very expensive one.
OL,12,F"This just allows you to chemically
OL,13,Fmodify the edge of the cornea with an
OL,14,Fenzyme using an is very cheap -
OL,15,Frestoring the correct properties so
OL,16,Fthe stem cells that are already in the
OL,17,Fbody can behave correctly."
