OL,3,CPioneering treatment could save sight
OL,4,Cof chemical attack victims
OL,6,FWhile the team continue to look at
OL,7,Fwork which could transform the outcome
OL,8,Ffor victims of such attacks, it is
OL,9,Fhoped that the number of people
OL,10,Frequiring such treatment could be
OL,11,Freduced if the crime itself is curbed.
OL,13,FProfessor Connon added: "It's very
OL,14,Fquick to do and the affects are
OL,15,Fpermanent and life-changing, and long-
OL,16,Flasting."
